          <a href="https://millercenter.org/the-presidency/presidential-speeches/july-24-1967-address-after-ordering-federal-troops-detroit">Miller Center: July 24, 1967: Address After Ordering Federal Troops to Detroit, Michigan</a>
        </textarea>
